{"tid":2510408,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"Now新聞台工程人員索償案　官勸作供警長勿說謊：不要侮辱我的智慧","createTime":"2021-04-30T06:48:47.000Z","updateTime":"2021-05-02T04:52:50.000Z","uid":6497,"like":21,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":26,"replies":[{"pid":"dfa76594aea60b23cd4c6a527a046768abbb555e","tid":2510408,"uid":6497,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-30T06:48:47.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20210430/SVRWT2WVIVDMFPK5G72IVQ2GHI/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20210430%2FSVRWT2WVIVDMFPK5G72IVQ2GHI%2F&d=SQXEpmicj55cx%2FeODTqnTyLieoVo5Z%2Bt8AyiqwqBN0Y%3D&h=1275707a\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20210430%2FSVRWT2WVIVDMFPK5G72IVQ2GHI%2F&h=7fb5a0ef\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20210430/SVRWT2WVIVDMFPK5G72IVQ2GHI/</a><br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/cnk_4SEyj6uWe8gTsWk2ErM9QR0=/802x451/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/WQ7XRV7THRGYDDKOORWL26N74A.JPG\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2Fcnk_4SEyj6uWe8gTsWk2ErM9QR0%3D%2F802x451%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2FWQ7XRV7THRGYDDKOORWL26N74A.JPG&h=9ebf91bb&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\nNow新聞台工程人員李小龍2014年採訪佔旺期間遭警員搶梯及暴力對待，事後入稟向警方索償。審訊踏入第14天，被指搶梯的警長繼續接受原告一方盤問，對當日爭執細節多次表示「唔確定」。主審區域法院法官李樹旭不滿警長看過庭上播放影片及相片後，仍未記起案發幾秒間發生的事，警告警長謂若不誠實作供，終會被發現，更嚴斥：「不要侮辱我的智慧。」「不要令警隊蒙羞。」警長則表示明白並堅稱：「我一直講緊正確嘅嘢。」<br />\n<br />\n律政司一方繼續由大律師黃紀怡代表，而原告人李小龍則由資深大律師林孟達代表。<br />\n<br />\n現為偵緝警長的潘景臨接受原告一方盤問。原告向他展示數張相片，顯示潘當時向前移動，但右手伸向後並呈握拳動作，右手位置亦從鋁梯尾部移至頂部。原告一方大律師質疑潘當時正在「搶梯」。<br />\n<br />\n潘否認謂：「我隻手係向後伸，但我冇揸住堂梯。」潘又反問：「原告人當時喺我後面，我點知佢有堂梯伸向我呢？」潘又解釋右手有移動是「拍攝角度問題」。"},{"pid":"15cbf939d5c8dc34d66ae67552b2c749df64442e","tid":2510408,"uid":230530,"like":11,"dislike":2,"score":9,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-04-30T06:54:37.000Z","msg":"法官可以調去守水塘"},{"pid":"453c5407775acfcc7458755209659dbff8a48766","tid":2510408,"uid":53498,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2021-04-30T06:58:24.000Z","msg":"罪名成立,但無處罰"},{"pid":"88aa68fee1d653d5a326620472debcab4c2da455","tid":2510408,"uid":39710,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-04-30T06:59:00.000Z","msg":"隻黑狗擺明鳩up啦"},{"pid":"0834b0224ce98851f247604da07702890903e2da","tid":2510408,"uid":77196,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-30T06:59:04.000Z","msg":"法官已犯國安法"},{"pid":"8df85fe89ce4d0356501a470714c377e0883c694","tid":2510408,"uid":306614,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"88aa68fee1d653d5a326620472debcab4c2da455","tid":2510408,"uid":39710,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-04-30T06:59:00.000Z","msg":"隻黑狗擺明鳩up啦"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-30T07:01:50.000Z","msg":"明顯黑警又嚟屈人"},{"pid":"25349120c55abe05e0924828935201cb595ac50c","tid":2510408,"uid":998,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-04-30T07:02:10.000Z","msg":"說謊咪說謊 最多訓斥下姐嘛"},{"pid":"6b5e02b79a736f8d44a45ed25f548ce872682273","tid":2510408,"uid":19552,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-30T07:02:32.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"12b2d76599dfa2deebc48e88da7cbb7eb1c1e362","tid":2510408,"uid":29874,"like":3,"dislike":1,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-04-30T07:06:18.000Z","msg":"已經無咗老防同埋藐視法庭<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />個官剩係話兩句了事，香港有法治真係得啖笑<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c31b07daa4c7f7eb52b81e0285a8812905ad6808","tid":2510408,"uid":44209,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-30T07:07:08.000Z","msg":"呢單應該已有結果<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/math.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c3e03947b3d33179dcc70b5220bc09a78da45880","tid":2510408,"uid":282347,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"15cb